data.description: ****** ADORABLE IN EVERY WAY ******* This quaint side-street location, square ranch lives large with an attached enclosed porch and great yard space.  In addition, there's a one car detached garage, full basement, hardwood floors and great storage. This family has lovingly made many recent updates and some major improvements over the years (roof, windows, heating, updated kitchen).  Appears to be FHA compliant, maintenance free siding, one-level living.  Washer/dryer included.  Second bathroom in the basement and yard, free-standing mason fireplace have not been used in many years so seller gives no warranty on such.  Seeking buyer with flexibility to close mid to end August. Commuters, this is a quick access to route 495 or easy drive to Franklin commuter station.   Someone is going to win big!!!!!
